                                <strong>I agree to the terms of this Non-Disclosure Agreement</strong>
                                <small>By checking this box and sending, I acknowledge that my digital signature has the same legal effect as a handwritten signature. Liz's counter-signature will be automatically applied upon submission.</small>
                            </span>
                        </label>
                    </div>

                    <div class="modal-actions">
                        <button class="btn btn-secondary" onclick="goToStep(1)">‚Üê Back</button>
                        <button class="btn btn-success" id="sendBtn" onclick="sendSignature()" disabled>
                            ‚úì Send Signed NDA
