                            </ul>
                        </div>

                        <div class="next-steps-info">
                            <h4>üöÄ What Happens Next?</h4>
                            <p>You can now access confidential report materials. The <strong>Document Review</strong> workflow card is now unlocked on your dashboard.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="download-options">
                        <button class="btn btn-secondary" onclick="viewFinalNDA()">
                            üëÅÔ∏è View NDA
                        </button>
                        <button class="btn btn-secondary" onclick="downloadFinalNDA()">
                            üíæ Download NDA
